items.title: International Business Machines (NYSE:IBM) Powers AI Innovation For Mitsubishi's New Outlander 2025
items.description: Mitsubishi Motor Sales of Canada recently launched "The Intelligent Companion," an AI-powered tool developed in collaboration with IBM's Watsonx, designed to enhance customer engagement with the Mitsubishi Outlander 2025. This innovation spotlights IBM's strength in integrating AI solutions with client businesses, and could have supported a positive sentiment towards International Business Machines (NYSE:IBM), reflected in the 12.87% share price increase over the last quarter.
